  "prompt": "What is the weather in orlando like in January?",
  "response": "In January, Orlando typically experiences mild and comfortable weather. Average daytime temperatures usually range from about 60\u00b0F to 70\u00b0F (15\u00b0C to 21\u00b0C), while nighttime temperatures can drop to around 40\u00b0F to 50\u00b0F (4\u00b0C to 10\u00b0C). Rainfall is relatively low during this month, and sunny days are common, making it a popular time for visitors to enjoy outdoor activities and theme parks. However, occasional cooler fronts can bring lower temperatures, so it's a good idea to pack layers.",
